{"tid":1422521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"諗到方法精神虐待班cosplayer","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:45:19.000Z","uid":18936,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a43383c6ab70faf47be6552f3097442120a935d2","tid":1422521,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"我見好多人都話希望暫停勇武 俾時間前線回氣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但咁樣咪即係俾時間班畜生回氣？</span></span><br />\n當然唔撚俾佢地抖啦<br />\n<br />\n我自己有個諗法 就係要令到佢地繼續否定自己 懷疑人生<br />\n方法就要靠文宣:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喺班畜生平時行咇寫薄仔啲箱附近貼poster</span></span> <br />\n內容大概可以有<br />\n1. 過街老鼠 xx區唔歡迎你呀！<br />\n2. 諗吓點解完成operation後唔係得到市民嘅歡呼聲<br />\n    而係噓聲啦<br />\n3. 除咗恰老弱婦孺你仲識啲咩<br />\n4. 黑社會<br />\nEtc 大家有idea可以再拋<br />\n<br />\n主要目的係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喺前線回氣同時<br />\n唔俾敵人休息</span></span>"},{"pid":"b61f4eef3867d9245d205b75788a9e82268865f0","tid":1422521,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"自推十下！"},{"pid":"fd439280d8e12a91a6b8d66487162c64d28686af","tid":1422521,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:07:16.000Z","msg":"自推十下！"},{"pid":"ad4af3b6eefc1f44a8fa2733fa279e9d551cf72a","tid":1422521,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"自推十下！"},{"pid":"4538bef642859750789339a959f72fb14c6af1d0","tid":1422521,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:07:40.000Z","msg":"自推十下！"},{"pid":"2d97e51a2b86f1fedfe1e3633957f31d6c62748d","tid":1422521,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"自推十下！"},{"pid":"c3f20e945f7ef73d9d49867049a482c99ce94800","tid":1422521,"uid":18936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:08:15.000Z","msg":"自推十下！"},